Title: New extended search dialog for rulesets and rules
Level: 2
Component: wato
Compatible: compat
Version: 1.4.0b1
Date: 1482137553
Class: feature

In addition to the longer existing quick search field, we have now added a
dedicated extended search dialog which you can access from the ruleset
listing pages. You can use it to search for nearly all aspects of rulesets
and rules.
